* This ISO-hybrid available for [download](http://download.webconverger.com/) can be treated as either a [[ISO]] or [[USB]] image

# Hardware

Webconverger works with **almost any standard x86 PC hardware** with at least 1G of RAM.

# Configuration management is a commerical product

<http://webconverger.com> is a UK & Singapore registered company that powers
this project.  The money generated through subscriptions is the fuel.

There is a [configuration service](http://config.webconverger.com/faq) and
email support service to help you get your PCs up and running with
Webconverger.

